    slug: 'bathroom-childproofing-toddler-falls-burns-poisons',
    title: 'Beyond the Tub: Comprehensive Bathroom Childproofing to Prevent Toddler Falls, Burns & Poisons',
    category: 'Fire Safety',
    excerpt: 'Go beyond water safety! Discover a comprehensive guide to childproofing your entire bathroom, preventing common toddler accidents like falls, burns, and accidental poisonings.',
    metaDescription: 'Go beyond water safety! Discover a comprehensive guide to childproofing your entire bathroom, preventing common toddler accidents like falls, burns, and accidental poisonings.',
    readTime: 6,
